Control different stepmotors.
D0:D3
bipolar 2 coil: mode0,mode1 D0:D2 coil1 D1:D3 coil2 (via LM298 or so)
monopolar 4 coil: D0:D1:D2:D3

Optocouplers suggested.

Modes: (var 'm')
 0: 4-phases half-step
 1: 4-phases full-step
 2: 3-phases half-step
 3: 3-phases full-step



Used USART2 with USB_UART board.
A2  = USART2_TX
A3  = USART2_RX

